# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout, so line
# endings are deterministic across Windows developers and the Linux CI runner
# (Prettier runs with endOfLine: "lf"). The index is already LF, so this adds
# no churn; it removes the reliance on each contributor's core.autocrlf setting.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
